# 📌 About This Repository

This repository is maintained by the HDO PRO community for informational, archival, and historical reference purposes only.

**This is NOT an official HDO Box repository.**

The purpose of this repository is to preserve publicly available information, installation guides, version history, and community notes related to the HDO TV application.

