# 📝 Community Notes

Community discussions indicate that HDO TV has existed as a dedicated Android TV build for several years and is separate from the mobile version. Users commonly install it through Downloader on Fire TV and Android TV devices.

Because information changes frequently, archived versions and installation methods may not always remain available.

